text.tspan: China and Russia veto draft resolution
Kofi Annan appointed joint UN−Arab League special envoy to Syria
Annan's ceasefire plan comes into force
Lakhdar Brahimi, joint UN−Arab League Special Representative begins his work; Annan quits; Ghouta chemical attack
UNSC resolution 2118 on the use of chemical weapons in Syria adopted
Fighting between ISIS and other rebel groups; Geneva II conference starts
Kurdish fighters repel ISIS from Kobane
Russia starts airstrikes against anti−Assad forces
